glish Church, 940–1154''. Series ''The Medieval World''. Harlow. {{ISBN|0-582-30303-6}}. *2007. "Anglo-Saxon England." In ''A century of British medieval studies'', ed. Alan Deyermond. British Academy centenary monographs. Oxford: OUP, 2007. 7–26.
